# Glassbox

**See Your AI Costs in Real-Time**

The terminal tool that makes AI development transparent. See every call, track every cost, catch every failure. One command, zero config, local-first.

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![Python 3.8+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
[![Code style: black](https://img.shields.io/badge/code%20style-black-000000.svg)](https://github.com/psf/black)

**Trust Signals:**
- ‚úÖ **Open Source** - [View Source](https://github.com/HudsonBales/glassbox) (MIT License)
- ‚úÖ **Local-First** - Data stays on your machine
- ‚úÖ **No Telemetry** - Zero data collection
- ‚úÖ **Production-Safe** - Never breaks your code
- ‚úÖ **Transparent** - You see everything we do

Run `glassbox trust` to see full trust guarantees.

## üöÄ Quick Start (2 Minutes)

### Install from PyPI

```bash
pip install glassbox-sdk
```

### Or Install from Source

If you want the latest development version:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/HudsonBales/glassbox.git
cd glassbox/sdk/python
pip install -e .
```

### Initialize
```bash
glassbox init
```

### Use
```python
import glassbox
glassbox.init()  # That's it!

# Your existing AI code works as-is
from openai import OpenAI
client = OpenAI()
response = client.chat.completions.create(...)
# ‚úÖ Automatically tracked!
```

### View Your Costs
```bash
glassbox live    # See costs in real-time
glassbox stats   # View statistics
```

**üéâ Done! You can now see your AI costs in real-time!**

üëâ **New user?** See [docs/NEW_USER_GUIDE.md](docs/NEW_USER_GUIDE.md) for complete walkthrough.

---

## Features

- üöÄ **One-line setup**: `glassbox.init(API_KEY)` - Works with ANY AI tech stack
- üåê **Universal compatibility**: HTTP interception, decorators, auto-wrapping, manual API
- üí∞ **Cost tracking**: Real-time cost monitoring with spike detection
- ‚ö° **Latency monitoring**: Track response times
- ‚úì **Validity checks**: Automatic output validation
- üìä **Prompt drift detection**: Alerts for performance degradation
- üì± **Local-first**: SQLite storage - all data stays on your machine
- üì∫ **CLI tool**: `glassbox live` for instant log viewing
- üéØ **Smart insights**: Cost spikes, failing prompts, performance alerts
- üìä **Real-time metrics**: See costs, latency, and validity as they happen
- üé® **Demo mode**: Auto-generates sample data so you can explore immediately

## Universal AI Stack Support

Glassbox works with **ANY AI tech stack** using multiple strategies:

1. **HTTP Interception** - Automatically tracks ANY HTTP-based AI API
2. **Auto-Wrapping** - Zero-config for OpenAI, Anthropic, LangChain
3. **Decorators** - User-controlled tracking for custom functions
4. **Manual API** - Full control when needed

See [docs/UNIVERSAL_INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md](docs/UNIVERSAL_INTEGRATION_GUIDE.md) for details.

